database.name: dphipdb
database.type: Oracle - Oracle Database 12c Standard Edition Release 12.2.0.1.0 - 64bit Production

table.name: TARGET_FORMS_VIEW
table.viewSql: ( SELECT tf.id AS target_form_id, t.gene_symbol AS gene_symbol, t.nurix_alias AS nurix_alias, t.uniprot_accession_id AS uniprot_accession_id FROM campaign_planning.target_forms tf, campaign_planning.targets t WHERE tf.target_id = t.id )
